{
  "stem": "9503.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So they put up storefronts of clothing and shoes, and people would recognize their possessions in those windows of the stuff that we had to leave in the-- in the cattle cars when we came in.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But you couldn't buy anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They put sausages.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I remember there was one storefront that was sausages hanging in the window, and we would take turns looking at them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, this was all pretend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then the minute that the Red Cross Commission left-- and they were-- they were-- how shall we say-- they appeared to be convinced that the Nazis were good to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it seems to me almost ludicrous that they couldn't look past that, and maybe they didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I don't know whether they didn't want to look past it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But then after they left, everything went back to normal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but I do remember that shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was warm water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And otherwise, I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got a-- a feather quilt as a cover, and I'm sure it came from somebody who had died.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember having a little pillow, and I had a-- you know, the mattresses were-- were straw-covered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, stuff like changing sheets?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were no sheets to change.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But to some-- that didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, it-- it must have been extremely-- I mean, we must have been dirty like-- like alley kids.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But that can wash off again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- as I mentioned, I-- I had an aunt who explained my-- my like for colognes as trying to get a smell out of my nose.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it must have been awful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It really must have been awful.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
